Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.45,0:00:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据生体数据的对比结果
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.49,0:00:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判断为绢江·克洛斯罗德小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请确认
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.46,0:00:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.58,0:02:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是吠陀的本体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.18,0:02:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚·修亨伯格…不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.36,0:02:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being的计划本身的系统
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.89,0:02:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行么  李本兹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.12,0:02:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要稍微花点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.58,0:02:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯纳家为了这一刻已经等了200多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.91,0:02:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯  用吠陀把攻击Trinity的部队的图像调出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话  从这里把那资料…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在屏蔽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:02:57.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:02:59.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下载完成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示影像
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.39,0:03:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种机体是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是拟太阳炉搭载型
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战火正在扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:20.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,0)}非洲大陆  西北部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:23.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗  还没和拉古那取得联系么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.06,0:03:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:27.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合国的新型号也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:29.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰哥  我们该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,状况如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在Level 5  Clear
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始Level 6的控制作业
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:48.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.51,0:03:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得无聊的话  看看这样的情报怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.49,0:03:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉古那·哈贝完成了GN-X的配置吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  他的任务到此为止了么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:09.56,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}联合  高轨道空间站
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:15.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  你是Flag Fighter吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我都不知道  你是在装吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AEU的王牌飞行员  帕特里克·克拉萨乌大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:31.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉萨乌？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:32.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:36.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  第一个被Gundam介入  被整得一塌糊涂的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要翻我旧账
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  联合的Top Gun在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾卡上级大尉不参加本次作战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:47.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.37,0:04:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吓成胆小鬼了么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:55.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合的王牌飞行员也没…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:04:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许你诬蔑我们队长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反…反对暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的部下失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是联合的达利尔·道奇准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.13,0:05:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是AEU的卡蒂·马内金上校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责本次作战的指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教  准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  必将全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待你的战果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕特里克  过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:25.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会有战果的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话  不飞Flag的意义就没了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没脸再见队长了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  这么勉强你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  谢谢帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:01.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是任务嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统的构筑状态呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成八成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这样行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.15,0:06:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把吠陀对Gundam的辅助切断的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.03,0:06:16.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机师的负担会…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.93,0:06:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不是酒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近变得柔和了哦  菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:35.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好倾向  好倾向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  拜托你们了  再加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从情报来看  吠陀的系统被什么人利用这点可以肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.13,0:07:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在没有吠陀的情况下与同型机对抗  能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:04.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有烦心的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩·斯托拉托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.39,0:07:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使没有吠陀的辅助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有Gundam和皇小姐的战术预报
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还不知道吧  她过去曾犯下的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.38,0:07:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.95,0:07:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都会犯错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她或许曾犯下了非常大的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而她为了偿还过去才选择了战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.88,0:07:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用酒精平息受创伤的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到这点的  也只有人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  洛克恩  我的事情你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.68,0:07:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位  皇小姐指示要我们到货柜待机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:55.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:08:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亚  我只说一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.78,0:08:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因为现在状况正在恶化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:06.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4部Gundam的配合才更为重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  这些话对刹那·F·清荣去说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:17.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索兰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:00.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜·伊斯迈尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这边来  索兰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:15.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
